vim

Description:
SearchAndReplace

:s/foo/bar/g   -> Change each 'foo' to 'bar' in the current line
:s/foo/bar     -> Change first 'foo' to 'bar' in the current line
:%s/foo/bar/g  -> Change each 'foo' to 'bar' in the current file
:%s/foo/bar/gc -> Change each 'foo' to 'bar' in the current file,
                  but ask for confirmation first